Hello Rahul,

Greetings from PharmEasy!

With regards to promotional notifications, we always try to keep our customers updated on our offers. However, we apologise for the inconvenience caused due to our promotional messages.

Please be assured, I have forwarded your request to unsubscribe your number '9552657226' from getting the promotional notifications. It will take 3 working days to process it completely. You will only receive your order-related information. Also, if you have a dual sim phone, I would request you to help us with the second number as well. We will forward a request for the other number as well. 

Further, to unsubscribe from getting the promotional notifications on your email id, I request you to open your latest promotional email and hit unsubscribe at the bottom right-hand side corner to stop email promotions.

I certainly hope this helps, and I appreciate your understanding and patience in the meantime.

For any further assistance, please reach out to us through our support channels in the App or website listed in the Need Help section.

Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Stay healthy!

Regards,
Habiba
